<a href="Controller?command=menuManage">메뉴 관리하기</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href="Controller?command=home">뒤로가기</a>
</center>
</div>
</body>
</html>